This paper deals with the placement of drone-BSs in wireless networks, which involves network optimization and control. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves the use of heuristic algorithms for optimization, which falls under the category of cs.RO (Robotics). Additionally, the paper deals with information theory and communication systems, which are covered by cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also involves system modeling and control, which falls under the category of cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper proposes a method for finding the optimal placement of drone-BSs, which involves artificial intelligence techniques, which are covered by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
